com.google.gwt.dev.cfg
Class PropertyPermutations

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gwt.dev.cfg.PropertyPermutations
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.String[]>
public class PropertyPermutations
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.String[]>

Generates all possible permutations of properties in a module. Each permutation consists of the list of active property values associated with that permutation. That list of property values is represented as an array of Strings corresponding to the list of properties returned by Properties.getBindingProperties().
